nodes.text: Olivia Hack is an American voice actress who voiced Katooni in Star Wars: The Clone Wars. She is best known for providing the voice of Rhonda Wellington Lloyd in the cartoon Hey Arnold! and for playing young Cindy Brady in the films The Brady Bunch Movie (1995) and A Very Brady Sequel (1996). She later voiced Qi'ra in Star Wars: Forces of Destiny.
